description: Highly sought after 3 bed/2 bath penthouse duplex w/ 4 private decks & 2 car parking in South Boston, one block from the beach. Enter to an oversized living room streaming natural light & impressive 17 ft vaulted ceilings. Living room flows into dining area that easily accommodates a table for 8 w/ private deck - perfect for indoor/outdoor entertaining. Kitchen boasts S/S appliances, quartz counters, abundant storage & wine fridge. The 1st floor is complete w/ a large bedroom w/ wall of closets, a full bath & laundry room. Top floor features a large loft space perfect for a home office & gym area. 2nd spacious BR hosts a large closet & private balcony. King-size 3rd bedroom offers plenty of storage & is adjacent to 2nd full bath. This home is complete with a common roof deck w/ sweeping City views, in-unit W/D, central air, hardwood floors throughout, large exterior storage, 4 decks & 2 car pkg. Live moments to Castle Island, parks, restaurants & the best South Boston has to offer.
